# notectl - Quick note-taking from terminal

> macOS command-line utility (Rust)

## Project Overview

**Type:** Command-line utility (Rust)
**Purpose:** Quick note-taking from terminal
**Platform:** macOS (Apple Silicon & Intel)

## Features

- Rapid note creation
- Tag-based organization
- Full-text search
- Note listing and filtering
- Export to Markdown
- Sync with cloud storage

## Development

```bash
# Build
cargo build

# Run
cargo run -- [ARGS]

# Test
cargo test

# Format and lint
cargo fmt
cargo clippy

# Build release
cargo build --release
```

## Installation

```bash
# Install locally
cargo install --path .

# Build and copy to system
cargo build --release
cp target/release/notectl /usr/local/bin/
```

## Usage

```bash
# Show help
notectl --help

# Show version
notectl --version
```
